OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA band of cloud and rain will
OL,6,Fpass over Orkney in the early morning
OL,7,Fwith the rain becoming patchy before
OL,8,Fcrossing Shetland in the early
OL,9,Fafternoon. Sunny spells with the odd
OL,10,Fshower will follow from the south.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FCloud and showers will
OL,13,Fincrease over Orkney from the evening,
OL,14,Fthe showers will clear towards
OL,15,Fmidnight. Shetland will stay dry
OL,16,Fovernight, bright at first becoming
OL,17,Fcloudy from late evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
