OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FThe day will be cloudy but
OL,6,Fmostly dry. Patchy rain may reach
OL,7,FOrkney for a time in the early
OL,8,Fafternoon and Shetland in the late
OL,9,Fafternoon.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FCloud
OL,12,Fand rain will clear north Sunday
OL,13,Fafternoon. Bright or sunny spells will
OL,14,Ffollow through the rest of the period
OL,15,Fwith showers at times. Breezy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
